# Deny-by-default: never commit anything in secrets/ unless whitelisted below.
# This protects bare-name plaintext files (e.g. `litellm-master-key`) produced
# by `scripts/decrypt-secrets.sh` from accidentally being committed.
*

# Encrypted secrets ARE committed.
!*.sops
!sa-keys/
!sa-keys/*.sops

# Documentation / placeholder files (no secret material).
!README.md
!.gitignore
!*.template.txt
